highlights.text: “Carol of the Bells” by Mykola Dmytrovych Leontovych and John Williams is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 93 spots at #104.
“Bartier Cardi (feat. 21 Savage)” by Cardi B and 21 Savage is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #54.
“Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 53 weeks straight.
